name: SIGIL OF VIOLENCE
description:
Pulsating red, overflowing with blood and pumping with adrenaline, violence consumes us in our most primitive moments,
and whether you like it or not violence is an integral part of existence since the dawn of time and all animals and humans on earth are susceptible to it.
Give in to it, feel it course through you and enjoy its power. 
800x800gif made on a Deluxe Paint emulator for the MS-DOS
